{
  "stem": "8.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was for the-- for the German army, for the Nazi war machine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were to do some kind of airplane parts, which had to be always like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] scraped and then put together and tested with some pressure, put together little parts with some spring and test it whether it would hold up.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother became like an overseer that we did the job well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we all worked together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We worked from 7 o'clock-- or 6 o'clock we arrived-- 6 o'clock until noon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were not allowed to get up to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And often we were in terrible pain trying to hold back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some people found some empty cans and used it under the table, but they would be punished if they were noted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the-- then in the afternoon we worked until 7 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At noon, we got our lunch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was our main meal, which was usually something that, by this time, I learned to love and looking forward to it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a concoction of some kind of gray material.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know what it was, some barley stuff in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember they also have some parsnip, which to this day I could not eat anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The work was terrible, because anytime they could find something wrong that we did, and we would be whipped and beaten for it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in spite of this, when we became better, we sabotaged the work and allowed many of the parts to go through, even though they did not fit.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't know-- I-- to this day I can't understand how we dared to do that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, there were also air raids in this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one day we were down in the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
